message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you this great product for $145. Let me know if you're interested!
Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I was thinking more along the lines of $130. Would you be willing to sell it to me for that price?
Hi Bob, I understand your budget constraints, but the lowest I can go is $140. Let me know if this works for you!
Hi Alice, I appreciate you coming down to $140, but I'm still a bit short. Would you be willing to meet me in the middle at $135?
Hi Bob, I can see you're trying to find a middle ground. I'm willing to come down a bit more to $138. Is this something you can work with?
